---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | CryptoBonusWorld"
  description="Learn how CryptoBonusWorld uses affiliate and referral links, how commissions work, and why exchange bonus terms may vary."
  canonical="/affiliate-disclosure/"
>
  <div class="container ad-container">
    <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Affiliate Disclosure' },
    ]} />

    <div class="ad-header">
      <h1 class="ad-h1">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="ad-intro">
        CryptoBonusWorld is an independent affiliate website. This page explains how we earn compensation,
        how that may affect what you see on the site, and what you should know before using any exchange link or promo code.
      </p>
      <p class="ad-meta">Last updated: June 2026 · <a href="/" class="ad-back">← Back to homepage</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="ad-prose">

      <h2>How We Earn Compensation</h2>
      <p>
        Some links on CryptoBonusWorld are affiliate or referral links. When you register on a crypto exchange
        through one of these links, we may earn a commission from that exchange. Compensation may take the form of:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Revenue share (RevShare)</strong> — a percentage of trading fees generated by referred users.</li>
        <li><strong>Cost-per-acquisition (CPA)</strong> — a fixed amount per qualifying registration, KYC completion, or first deposit.</li>
        <li><strong>Hybrid arrangements</strong> combining RevShare and CPA elements.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These arrangements are between CryptoBonusWorld and the exchange. <strong>There is no extra cost to you.</strong>
        Exchange fees, trading rates, and bonus terms are the same whether you arrive via our link or directly.
      </p>

      <h2>How This May Affect Our Content</h2>
      <p>Affiliate relationships may influence:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Which exchanges are featured on this website.</li>
        <li>The order in which exchanges appear in listings or comparison tables.</li>
        <li>The prominence given to specific bonus offers.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Affiliate relationships do <strong>not</strong> affect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The factual accuracy of bonus data, promo codes, or terms we publish.</li>
        <li>Our editorial assessments of exchange limitations or risks.</li>
        <li>Our decision to include conditions, restrictions, and cons for every exchange.</li>
        <li>Our compliance with applicable disclosure requirements.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We only list exchanges we consider reputable. We do not promote exchanges with documented withdrawal fraud,
        widespread unresolved user complaints, or significant regulatory violations.
      </p>

      <h2>About Exchange Bonus Amounts</h2>
      <div class="ad-callout">
        <p>
          <strong>Welcome bonus figures are advertised maximums, not typical results.</strong>
          Reaching the headline amount usually requires completing a series of tasks — such as depositing above a threshold,
          trading a minimum volume, and finishing all tasks within a time window (often 30 days after registration).
        </p>
      </div>
      <p>
        Bonus availability and amounts can vary based on:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Country and residency</strong> — some offers are not available in certain regions due to local regulations or exchange licensing.</li>
        <li><strong>Account verification (KYC)</strong> — most exchanges require identity verification to unlock or withdraw bonus value.</li>
        <li><strong>Deposit and trading requirements</strong> — different bonus tiers unlock at different deposit or volume thresholds.</li>
        <li><strong>Offer terms and expiry</strong> — promotions can change or expire. The terms shown on the official exchange website take precedence.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Most welcome bonuses are issued as trading fee vouchers or conditional credits — <strong>not withdrawable cash</strong>.
        The actual value depends on your trading activity after signup.
      </p>

      <h2>Identifying Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        All "Claim Bonus" buttons and exchange registration links on CryptoBonusWorld are affiliate referral links.
        These links use internal redirect paths (e.g. <code>/go/bybit/</code>) to route you to the exchange's official website.
        They are labelled as affiliate links on each exchange page.
      </p>

      <h2>Not Financial or Investment Advice</h2>
      <div class="ad-callout ad-callout--warn">
        <p>
          CryptoBonusWorld provides informational content about crypto exchange promo codes and referral bonuses.
          <strong>Nothing on this site constitutes financial, investment, legal, or tax advice.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
      <p>
        Cryptocurrency trading involves significant financial risk. Exchange bonuses do not reduce that risk.
        The value of cryptocurrencies can decrease as well as increase. Past exchange performance does not indicate future results.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Responsibility</h2>
      <p>Before registering on any exchange through our links, you should:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Read the exchange's full terms and conditions, including the bonus program terms.</li>
        <li>Verify the current promo code and bonus offer directly on the official exchange website.</li>
        <li>Check whether the exchange and its bonus offer are available in your country.</li>
        <li>Ensure you meet KYC and other eligibility requirements.</li>
        <li>Consider your own financial situation and risk tolerance before depositing funds.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Keeping Information Up to Date</h2>
      <p>
        We aim to keep promo codes and bonus terms accurate. Exchange promotions change frequently — if you notice
        outdated information, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a> and we will review and update the relevant page.
        Always verify current conditions on the official exchange website before making a decision.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about our affiliate relationships or how they affect our content,
        please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
      </p>

      <p class="ad-updated"><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .ad-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .ad-header {
    margin: 16px 0 36px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border, #E5E7EB);
    padding-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .ad-h1 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary, #111827);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -.02em;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .ad-intro {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #4B5563);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .ad-meta {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #6B7280);
  }

  .ad-back {
    color: var(--color-accent, #F7931A);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .ad-back:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .ad-prose {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #374151);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .ad-prose h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary, #111827);
    margin: 36px 0 12px;
    padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border, #F3F4F6);
  }
  .ad-prose h2:first-of-type { border-top: none; margin-top: 0; }

  .ad-prose p { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .ad-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .ad-prose ul {
    margin: 0 0 14px 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .ad-prose ul li {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .ad-prose code {
    font-family: 'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary, #F9FAFB);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #E5E7EB);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary, #111827);
  }

  .ad-prose a {
    color: var(--color-accent, #F7931A);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .ad-prose a:hover { opacity: .8; }

  .ad-callout {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary, #F9FAFB);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent, #F7931A);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  .ad-callout p { margin: 0; }
  .ad-callout--warn {
    border-left-color: #EF4444;
    background: #FFF5F5;
  }

  .ad-updated {
    margin-top: 40px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #9CA3AF);
  }
</style>
